# SMTP Configuration (Gmail — use an App Password, not your real password)
# 1. Enable 2-Step Verification: Google Account → Security → 2-Step Verification
# 2. Generate App Password: Google Account → Security → App Passwords → Create one for "Mail"
# 3. Paste the 16-character app password below (spaces are fine)
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your-gmail@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx
SMTP_FROM=AUSS <your-gmail@gmail.com>
